progression.synopsis: Sensei goes to visit Chinami again, although only after she promises to stop endangering him with talk about Chika having a baby. Chinami has been expanding her business activities , and they talk about what Chinami will do when she is rich. Chinami wants to go outside, which Sensei doesn't think is a good idea until Chinami corrects his misapprehension about how far.
